        "text": "## Result: No Stability Constant Found for Pu(IV) + Aspirin\n\n### Summary\n\nThe **NIST SRD-46 database does not contain a stability constant for plutonium(IV) with aspirin (acetylsalicylic acid, ligand_10913)**. A direct search for the Pu⁴⁺ / aspirin pair returned no measurements, and the ligand record for aspirin itself shows **zero VLM (value-measurement) entries** across all metals.",
